body.description: Wiggle away! OLLY Kids Multivitamin Gummy Worms are playful nutrient-packed gummies made with a complete blend of daily vitamins and minerals to help kiddos thrive and promote overall wellness. These OLLY Kids Vitamins deliver a daily dose of essential vitamins and minerals A, C, D, E, Bs and Zinc to support growing kiddos and fill the gaps when eating habits are less than perfect (because let’s face it, not all wiggle worms love to eat their veggies!). The chewable daily vitamin comes in a delicious Sour Fruity Punch flavor. Good health is at the center of everything we do. That's why we’ve made it our mission to make nutrition easy to understand. We do it by crafting products that are as effective as they are delicious—because we know when something feels good, you’re more likely to do it.* *These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Toddlers ask for them!
reviews.reviewText: I have been a longtime lover of Olly and recently started my two toddlers on this multivitamin. They both love the taste and are so excited to eat their vitamin each day. The quality is great - I’ve had other kids multivitamins that melted or stuck together and these stay separated.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Product is great - way it arrived was not..
reviews.reviewText: The product is great, but the way it was packaged was not. There were what looked like soft freezer packs in it and then they put them into a soft shipping bag....the packs burst (probably from being thrown around an amazon truck) and the gel was EVERYWHERE!! It took me forever to clean my counter top and the product, and I had to empty them into a container since the original packaging was still slimy.Maybe look into how you ship them, but otherwise love this product!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These improved my kids behavior
reviews.reviewText: This is one vitamin that my picky eaters actually would eat. Mind you, they would complain at times, but this is one that they would actually stomach. And I have to say, if you have any childhood behavioral issues, choosing a well-balanced multivitamin is something you should try. It made a difference for my eight year old.

reviews.reviewText: I read ingredients for my kids. Kids love that they resemble the candy and are eager to eat their vitamins first thing.
